<h1>Thank you for participating in our study. We have a few more questions for you...</h1>
<div>
  <p>How did you feel about the interaction method for viewing and selecting images?</p>
  <select id="interaction_rating">
    <option value="null"></option>
    <option value="1">Very Negative</option>
    <option value="2">Negative</option>
    <option value="3">Neutral</option>
    <option value="4">Positive</option>
    <option value="5">Very Positive</option>
  </select>
</div>

<div>
  <p>How helpful was the display method for completing the task?</p>
  <select id="display_helpfulness">
    <option value="null"></option>
    <option value="1">Very unhelpful</option>
    <option value="2">Unhelpful</option>
    <option value="3">Neutral</option>
    <option value="4">Helpful</option>
    <option value="5">Very helpful</option>
  </select>
</div>

<% if @model.get('experiment_group') != 1: %>
  <div>
    <p>How would you describe the experience of rapidly viewing images?</p>
    <textarea id='rsvp_experience'></textarea>
  </div>
<% end %>

<div>
  <p>Was there anything about the experience you found difficult?</p>
  <textarea id='experience_difficulty'></textarea>
</div>

<button type="button" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
